Package: mbhlcore
Type: Package
Title: MBHL Core — Database Infrastructure and Shared Utilities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Hugo", "Lepage",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "hugo_lep@hotmail.com"
  )
Description: Core infrastructure for the MBHL maintenance platform (AvnumbeRs).
    Provides PostgreSQL connectivity, versioned database migrations, shared entity
    definitions (aircraft, bases, personnel, companies, currencies), and permission
    management utilities shared by mbhlMaintenance, mbhlMagasin, and mbhlComptable.
